{"tid":2395545,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"big big shop購740元一盒澳洲車厘子　女事主：三日後驚見極速變爛","createTime":"2021-02-05T03:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T20:46:38.000Z","uid":66271,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"07461f6e689c6c79573b1ed51c3d111f551ae60f","tid":2395545,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2870000/2870935/bigbigshop_thumb_20210204_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2870000%2F2870935%2Fbigbigshop_thumb_20210204_ch_1024.jpg&h=e1784f61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車厘子近年成為熱賣年貨，但內地近日卻在進口車厘子上驗出新冠病毒，本港一名女子近日在網上論壇分享，稱在big big shop購買兩盒澳洲車厘子，而每盒740元，但3日後驚見車厘子極速變爛，她坦言中伏，以後都不幫襯big big shop。<br />\n<br />\n該名女事主日前在「親子王國」論壇圖文並茂發帖稱，因疫情關係不敢去果欄買水果， 第一次幫襯big big shop，買了兩盒澳洲塔斯曼尼亞車厘子，但車厘子竟然不新鮮，<br />\n<br />\n1月28號收貨開咗一盒已經淋淋地唔夠爽脆，1月31號開第二盒，竟然成盒都開始腐爛，740元一盒咁嘅質素，我以後都唔會幫襯！ <br />\n<br />\n帖文一出引起網民熱議，不少網民斥離譜，應要求退貨，「要求退貨啦...差成咁」；有網民稱，「哇，740蚊咁樣真係好嬲喎！可能送貨焗耐左所以易爛。」樓主回應稱，「我由收貨到今日都係四日，我諗佢唔係送貨焗爛，係本身批貨已經係熟到爛。」，並稱一向去果欄親自選水果，因疫情才不敢去，「諗住佢話係代理直送應該信得過，點知就中伏。」<br />\n<br />\nTOPick就事件向Big Big Shop查詢，Big Big Shop表示於1月31日接獲事主反映所購買的2盒車厘子出現不新鮮的情況，得悉其中一盒客人已存放三天。車厘子由商戶直送，相信有關情況是因天氣影響及運輸損耗所致。經磋商後，Big Big Shop已於2月2日按客人要求，承諾退回有關車厘子之款項。<br />\n<br />\nBig Big Shop會提醒商戶，必須確保貨品質素及注意運輸流程。另由於水果易受天氣或環境因素影響，Big Big Shop建議客人收到水果後盡快享用。<br />\n<br />\n據内地媒體近日報道，目前正在運載或已運抵上海、香港港口但尚未銷售的南美櫻桃，尚有約5,000櫃，共計10萬噸。有網民1月27日就在Facebook專頁「食在元朗」發帖分享，指元朗一間超市門外晚上突然大排長龍，至少有20、30人排隊，其後才知是一批新到貨車厘子劈價平賣，一磅僅售20元。價格雖然便宜，但仍有網民憂心車厘子會有新冠病毒。"},{"pid":"5d88ea2902a5fe05c791cdbf9b2017d355b64474","tid":2395545,"uid":391698,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:24:26.000Z","msg":"淘寶買咪冇事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c082ffcb3f001e43527bb6ee6851f56a3a167213","tid":2395545,"uid":27664,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"Big big shop用戶大大聲話以後都唔會幫襯喎，信你先奇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2110c1cc6d6aaf9a073e153b54cda185b5578976","tid":2395545,"uid":126382,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:47:10.000Z","msg":"藍絲抵撚死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54dedd207e8ccf5253dd35744d97d2b81bf00c9e","tid":2395545,"uid":195169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />BIG BIG SHOP係咁上下啦"},{"pid":"50e97243894809f9054585d224170c265697578f","tid":2395545,"uid":118754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:55:25.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<br />\n幫襯tvb<br />\n食撚死你"},{"pid":"9e37afdc1aa25d4f5d22e94bef478c1330fd1601","tid":2395545,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:35:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fed411a64fb686300382c7b0beee520d0c82904","tid":2395545,"uid":277578,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"依家都仲用big big shop嘅真係唔駛可憐。"},{"pid":"eee3cceb28999b912